<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mon Amour pour Toi ❤️</title>
    <style>
        /* --- STYLE GENERAL --- */
        body {
            background: radial-gradient(circle, #2c0001 0%, #000000 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            perspective: 1500px; /* Donne de la profondeur pour l'effet livre */
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* --- ENVELOPPE --- */
        .envelope-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            width: 350px;
            height: 230px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
            transition: all 1s ease;
        }

        /* Rabat supérieur */
        .envelope-wrapper::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; z-index: 4;
            border-top: 115px solid #f9f9f9;
            border-right: 175px solid transparent;
            border-left: 175px solid transparent;
            transform-origin: top;
            transition: transform 0.8s ease-in-out;
        }

        /* Corps avant de l'enveloppe */
        .envelope-wrapper::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; z-index: 2;
            border-top: 115px solid transparent;
            border-right: 175px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-bottom: 115px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-left: 175px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        /* Le Coeur central */
        .heart {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%; left: 50%; width: 40px; height: 40px;
            background: #d40000;
            z-index: 5;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(45deg);
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(212, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .heart::before, .heart::after {
            content: ""; position: absolute; width: 40px; height: 40px;
            background: #d40000; border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .heart::before { top: -20px; left: 0; }
        .heart::after { left: -20px; top: 0; }

        /* --- LA CARTE (LIVRE 3D) --- */
        .book {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px; left: 10px;
            width: 330px; height: 210px;
            background: white;
            z-index: 1;
            transform-style: preserve-3d;
            transition: all 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        .page {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            backface-visibility: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 30px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        /* Couverture du livre */
        .cover {
            background: #ffffff;
            z-index: 10;
            transform-origin: left;
            transition: transform 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.645, 0.045, 0.355, 1);
        }

        /* Page intérieure */
        .content {
            background: #fffafa;
            transform: rotateY(0deg); /* Elle est derrière la couverture */
            z-index: 9;
        }

        /* --- ANIMATIONS AU CLIC --- */
        .container.open .envelope-wrapper::before {
            transform: rotateX(180deg);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .container.open .heart {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translate(-50%, -250%) rotate(45deg);
        }

        /* La carte sort légèrement et s'agrandit */
        .container.open .book {
            transform: translateY(-120px) scale(1.2);
            z-index: 10;
        }

        /* La page du livre s'ouvre sur le côté */
        .container.open .cover {
            transform: rotateY(-160deg);
        }

        /* Style des textes */
        h2 { color: #d40000; font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: 1.8em; margin: 0; }
        p { color: #333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; }
        .signature { margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #d40000; font-style: italic; }

        /* Animation de flottement pour l'enveloppe au début */
        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }
        .container:not(.open) {
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <audio id="loveMusic" loop>
        <source src="https://www.soundhelix.com/examples/mp3/SoundHelix-Song-15.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
    </audio>

    <div class="container" id="cardContainer">
        <div class="envelope-wrapper">
            <div class="book">
                <div class="page cover">
                    <h2>Pour Ma Reine ❤️</h2>
                    <p>Une surprise t'attend à l'intérieur...</p>
                    <small style="color: #999;">(Touche pour ouvrir)</small>
                </div>
                <div class="page content">
                    <h3 style="color: #d40000;">Mon Amour,</h3>
                    <p>Comme dans une chanson de Dadju, tu es ma "Reine". Mon cœur ne bat que pour toi. Merci d'être la femme extraordinaire que tu es.</p>
                    <p class="signature">Je t'aime pour l'éternité.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="heart"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const container = document.getElementById('cardContainer');
        const music = document.getElementById('loveMusic');

        container.addEventListener('click', function() {
            // Activer les animations
            container.classList.add('open');
            
            // Jouer la musique
            music.volume = 0.5; // Volume modéré
            music.play().catch(e => console.log("L'audio attend un clic"));
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
